---
const footerLinks = [
	{ href: '/', label: 'Domov' },
	{ href: '/sluzby', label: 'Služby' },
	{ href: '/kontakt', label: 'Kontakt' },
];

const email = 'kontakt@elektronovak.sk';
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-100 bg-white dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-black">
	<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 sm:py-24" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
		<div
			class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-24 left-1/2 h-64 w-lg -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/10 blur-3xl dark:bg-yellow-400/10"
			aria-hidden="true"
		/>
		<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2
				id="cta-heading"
				class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl dark:text-white"
			>
				Poďme spolu vytvoriť niečo skvelé.
			</h2>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-lg dark:text-neutral-400">
				Napíšte nám a ozveme sa vám do 24 hodín. Bez zbytočných formulárov — priamo e-mailom.
			</p>
			<a
				href={`mailto:${email}`}
				class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-black shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-yellow-500"
			>
				Napíšte nám e-mail
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:py-10">
				<a
					href="/"
					class="flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 transition-colors hover:text-yellow-500 dark:text-white sm:text-xl"
				>
					<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
					</svg>
					Elektro Novák
				</a>

				<nav aria-label="Pätička navigácia">
					<ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2">
						{
							footerLinks.map((link) => (
								<li>
									<a
										href={link.href}
										class="rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition-colors hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-yellow-500 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white/5 dark:hover:text-yellow-400"
									>
										{link.label}
									</a>
								</li>
							))
						}
					</ul>
				</nav>

				<a
					href={`mailto:${email}`}
					class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition-colors hover:text-yellow-500 dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-yellow-400"
				>
					{email}
				</a>
			</div>
			<p class="pb-8 text-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-neutral-500 sm:pb-10">
				© 2026 Elektro Novák. Všetky práva vyhradené.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
